title: #92Noon! 10am Hour 11/24 - Whalen/Zimmer
description: Lindsay Whalen for a catchup, then some Vikings conversation including most of Mike Zimmer's press conference. The hour ends with some interesting audio from Aaron Rodgers about facing Mike Zimmer's defense and Harrison Smith's greatness.
